  "response": "The Yongnuo RF-603 II RF triggers do not support high-speed sync (HSS). They are basic radio triggers that allow for standard sync speeds, typically up to 1/200 or 1/250 of a second, depending on your camera's capabilities. \n\nIf you need HSS functionality, you would want to look for other Yongnuo products, such as the Yongnuo YN-622 series, which do support high-speed sync triggering. Always check the specifications and compatibility with your camera and flash to ensure they meet your needs.",
